What would you like?

689
01:30:42,340 --> 01:30:45,434
Another ice cream,
a pretty ring...

690
01:30:45,510 --> 01:30:47,307
and a parade.

691
01:30:49,514 --> 01:30:52,711
Here's the parade.

692
01:30:52,784 --> 01:30:54,945
ln any case,
it's time to leave.

693
01:31:01,293 --> 01:31:03,921
- Fall the company in.
- Sir!

694
01:31:05,096 --> 01:31:08,224
Company, fall in!

695
