On the double!

696
01:31:18,476 --> 01:31:21,036
Plumpick, fall in behind the church.

697
01:31:23,014 --> 01:31:25,073
l'll be waiting at Hyacinth's brothel.

698
01:31:25,984 --> 01:31:29,750
