to that...

737
01:39:58,830 --> 01:40:02,163
which the president
of the Republic sends you.

738
01:40:08,406 --> 01:40:12,240
Plumpick, you're going up
to the front again immediately.

739
01:40:13,444 --> 01:40:15,537
