744
01:41:35,159 --> 01:41:39,425
Well, you're here now.
And you won't be running off anymore.

745
01:41:39,497 --> 01:41:41,522
l'm staying here, General.

746
01:41:41,599 --> 01:41:44,261
- l'm not going anywhere.
